			<p>
				The first step in integrating the acquired product was to rebuild their non-performant javascript mobile app in native code. In order to quickly release a functional, reliable app, the app functionality and design remained similar to the existing app, with a reskin to RingCentral brand guidelines, and an addition of some usability enhancements that would improve the experience and feel native on iOS and Android.
