	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-md-10 col-centered">
			<h3>Process: Usability Improvements on iOS</h3>
			<p>
				A few of the usability enhancements I advocated are shown below.
			</p>
			<h4 class="indent-usability-header">Finding a Conversation</h4>
			<div class="col-md-5 col-md-offset-1">
				<div class="screenshots-before-after">
					<img src="/images/projects/glip-project/4-messages.png">
					<h4>BEFORE</h4>
				</div>
				<div class="before-after-list">
					<ul>
						<li>Finding a conversation required scrolling through a long list of names, and it was difficult to find a specific person.</li>
						<li>It was difficult to distinguish conversations with people I found important (ie. my Favorites) from those I thought were less important (ie. a team where lots of messages accumulated).</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="col-md-5">
				<div class="screenshots-before-after">
					<img src="/images/projects/glip-project/5-Messages_noframe.png">
					<h4>AFTER</h4>
				</div>
				<div class="before-after-list">
					<ul>
						<li>Filters at the top helped distinguish an individual conversation from a team conversation and quickly navigate to messages from my Favorites.</li>
						<li>Individual contact photos differed from a team or group conversation icon.</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-md-10 col-centered">
			<h4 class="indent-usability-header">Creating a New Message</h4>
			<div class="col-md-5 col-md-offset-1">
				<div class="screenshots-before-after">
					<img src="/images/projects/glip-project/6-start new message_select person.png">
					<h4>BEFORE</h4>
				</div>
				<div class="before-after-list">
					<ul>
						<li>Just to create a new message, users had to navigate through the entire company directory.</li>
						<li>Looking for my coworker, Sam would require scrolling through 300+ names first.</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="col-md-5">
				<div class="screenshots-before-after">
					<img src="/images/projects/glip-project/7- New Message Input Name.png">
					<h4>AFTER</h4>
				</div>
				<div class="before-after-list">
					<ul>
						<li>Suggested contacts were visible to help cue the user and to easily start a new message.</li>
						<li>Search allowed quickly finding a contact to start a message.</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

